# Deadline Telegram Bot

A Telegram bot designed to help students efficiently manage their deadlines and assignments, track grades, and calculate scholarship eligibility.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Demo](#demo)
- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
