- [License](#license)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [Acknowledgments](#acknowledgments)
- [Contact](#contact)

## Features

- Track assignment deadlines and receive reminders.
- Calculate required grades for scholarships based on midterm and end-term grades.
- User-friendly interaction via Telegram.
- Persistent data storage for user information and assignments.

