## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.x installed on your machine.
- A Telegram bot token (create a bot using [BotFather](https://core.telegram.org/bots#botfather)).
- Required Python packages (listed in `requirements.txt`).

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Jamsh1d05/deadline_tele_bot.git
   cd deadline_tele_bot
   pip install -r requirements.txt


### Commands

    /start: Initialize the bot and set up your account.
    /add_assignment: Add a new assignment and its due date.
    /check_deadlines: View upcoming assignment deadlines.
    /calculate_scholarship: Calculate the grades needed for scholarships.
    /help: Show available commands and usage instructions.

